Support files to build brickd for openwrt
-----------------------------------------
brickd.hotplug:
	this file is a hotplug2 script that sends an USR1 signal to the brickd when a brick is 
	connected or removed from the USB bus.
Makefile: 
	This is a OpenWRT package definition makefile that is needed to build brickd as an OpenWRT 
	package.
	To include this package into your OpenWRT build simply link or copy the /src/build_data/
	openwrt folder to your package directory of your OpenWRT build tree, select the brickd2
	package in the menuconfig and build. 
